{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"generate-id","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/generate-id","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>generate-id</code>関数は、指定されたノード集合の最初のノードの一意のIDを生成し、そのIDを含む文字列を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">generate-id( [<em>node-set</em>] )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"node-set\"><code><em>node-set</em></code> (任意)</dt>\n <dd>このノード集合の最初のノードに対してIDが生成されます。省略すると、現在のコンテキストノードが使用されます。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>生成されたIDを含む文字列。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注記","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>同じIDは、現在の変換で現在の文書の同じノードに対して毎回生成されなければなりません</li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n <li>生成されたIDは、その後の変換では同じではない可能性があります</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>この関数はXPathへのXSLT固有の追加です。コアXPath関数ライブラリの一部ではありません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xslt#function-generate-id\" rel=\" noopener\">XSLT 1.0 12.4</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko のサポート","isH3":true,"content":"<p>サポート済み</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"generate-id関数は、指定されたノード集合の最初のノードの一意のIDを生成し、そのIDを含む文字列を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"generate-id","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"generate-id","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"generate-id","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"generate-id","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/generate-id","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xpath/functions/generate-id/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/generate-id","title":"generate-id"}],"pageTitle":"generate-id - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}